{"tid":1435063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"4 POSTS整合 浸大被捕 巴打天橋被狗逗 撚狗或比狗撚","createTime":"2019-08-09T02:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T03:34:46.000Z","uid":28257,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"62f10a3111d66c2c50a0ef907b022efeb79750ba","tid":1435063,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:50:46.000Z","msg":"由於呢個係4 POSTS 的整合，可能有D混亂，故此請大家按時間線黎理解。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1BxCuSM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1BxCuSM.jpg&h=3a7d594d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1423591/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1423591/page/1</a> 撚狗POST 1 及2<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1433489/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1433489/page/1</a>  巴打朋友被兇POST 1<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1434132/page/1 \" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1434132/page/1 </a> 巴打朋友被兇POST 2<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OjM9aG3xZKk&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOjM9aG3xZKk%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzcorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=67bffcba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OjM9aG3xZKk&amp;feature=youtu.be</a> 巴打朋友被兇 片一<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F74MRhonX28&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DF74MRhonX28%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzcorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=2fa0af8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F74MRhonX28&amp;feature=youtu.be</a> 巴打朋友被兇 片二<br />\n<br />\n簡述如下，一開始，我尻UP左一個撚狗或比狗撚次序，重點就係，比狗逗，一定要要求睇委任證，大聲清楚咁讀資料出黎，必要者 &mdash; 姓名/警階/編號，比器材錄音，事後再尋親或上載。同晚浸大學生會長被捕。再過兩晚，就到巴打天橋被逗，比一班狗圍同恐嚇，好彩錄住影，班狗無所能之。<br />\n<br />\n好多人或問，整合POST的因由係咩? 因有三：撚狗POST中有多人質疑錄影的作用/可能性/因而惹禍上身被捉入狗屋；第二，巴打靠錄影自保左。第三，係巴打天橋被兇的片一，影片開頭馬上就有女警話：「小心錄音。」。<br />\n<br />\n希望藉巴打的親身經歷，一洗大家對錄影的懷疑心態。<br />\n好奇的係，錄音有咩好怕呢? 何解要小心呢? 大家心照。<br />\n<br />\n市民被截查個陣，與其話有權錄影，倒不用話狗無權 要求我地停錄。我地只需合作，合理合法咁配合佢地的查問/搜身就可以。除身分證所顯示的資料外，大家冇需多答。<br />\n<br />\n由此結論，警員對出示委任證/警員資料有所避諱。既然政府同大粒狗改變左策略，大家亦要作出相對的應對。每次截查都係我地以守為攻黃金機會，要好好把握。<br />\n<br />\n此9UP係指一般普通的街邊截查，並非鼓吹大家，對峙期間或示威現場，主動親身上前去逗狗。被狗強行拘捕，只會令自己身體難受，心緒受假控罪困擾。"},{"pid":"2b8af6b49404b66135f1267f97d0096471259d8a","tid":1435063,"uid":28257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:51:27.000Z","msg":"巴打個2個POSTS，以BULLET POINT 例舉重點，如下<br />\n<br />\n截查期間(STOP AND SEARCH)，不屬羈留。被捕後，入左狗屋先算羈留，先要跟命令。<br />\n<br />\n影片係財物之一，如相片，狗無權刪片 (90%真實，有待再查證)<br />\n<br />\n市民係可以係唔阻礙警方搜身時錄影 (底線，大家企硬)，警方需指出市民如何阻礙執行職務<br />\n<br />\n絲打 一雞死鳥山鳴 ：「今日個記招唔係話強行del人啲片屬於刑事毀壞&hellip;.」<br />\n巴打 &mdash; 我酸故我在開CAM 話: 「我而家拍緊呢條片, 唔排除用作新聞用途&hellip;..唔該唔好郁到/唔好阻礙拍攝」<br />\n<br />\n巴打&mdash; 戚家二少個潤: 比黑警截查時一定要拍片保命（最好就直播），唔好有任何動作，如果唔係就屈你襲警。保持冷靜，佢兇你唔洗驚由得佢屌，你拍住片，佢仲驚撚過你呀<br />\n<br />\n16歲以下兒童，無論是否涉及刑事，只應在兒童家長或監護人在場時才進行查問，校內，則必須教師或授權人士在場及同意下進行。"},{"pid":"7895adfa702b391287582f80f66b20f1c5877edd","tid":1435063,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:51:41.000Z","msg":"案例：許智峯奪去一名女行政主任政府手機，衝入男洗手間內17分鐘，用自己方法」記下手機中的資料。香港警方起訴許智峯3罪，包括普通襲擊、有犯罪或不誠實意圖取用電腦以及阻礙公職人員執行公務。2019年5月27日裁判官鄭念慈裁定許全部三項罪名成立。"},{"pid":"5937c2bc9a45f64fce3adf40d177d840afe453d6","tid":1435063,"uid":28257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:52:09.000Z","msg":"我的尻UP重點<br />\n<br />\n(請大家先睇左個POST先) <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1423591/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1423591/page/1</a><br />\n群眾/街坊/記者愈多，愈安全。<br />\n<br />\n錄影唔好解鎖手機，直接開CAMERA錄，直播更好。<br />\n<br />\n見到資料，要大聲清楚讀出黎<br />\n<br />\n正常情況，有掛狗牌係可以一覽五項資料：中英文名/性別/警階//警員編號/更換日期。換言之，係唔需詢問，直接肉眼睇得到。市民係亦有權得知行使緊警權的公僕的資料。<br />\n<br />\n以資料換資料黎應對<br />\n<br />\n被截查，我地的目的，係拎佢地的警員資料去尋親，合作配合查問，配以禮貌，係一個最殺其惜手不及的手段。一份資料都拎唔到，輸左! 拎左一份，嬴左2次!"},{"pid":"5dd7fd6cc19b7486b767712717b55550fbee172b","tid":1435063,"uid":56594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:55:47.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"1a01b184a5c074d79139a2df2e2493e30fdeda66","tid":1435063,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"331b3d5947dfde1cdd5758276b0aef2583bb4ed8","tid":1435063,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b5d06ff6a5bdac9058559db9eb641ecc4bf8c05","tid":1435063,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:58:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b240f05f8d5503bbc6da3782f547d4e3c98ca044","tid":1435063,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05283c51fc674b0a949ab8bdd2322fcff46f4ae","tid":1435063,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830b897995598bf841deba82dfc07436e3844f7a","tid":1435063,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:00:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9a08034d184a2e66ba1370e1c4e8369f77d79c0","tid":1435063,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNOxBrP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNOxBrP.gif&h=672c8b5c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bDJNqkb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbDJNqkb.gif&h=27f2be48&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://streamable.com/igroa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Figroa&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzcorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=3a92cf49\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/igroa</a></span><br />\nSSP , 06/08 , mid-night<br />\n行過想拉就拉 路人無故被捕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/N71O2ra.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN71O2ra.gif&h=0c7e59fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://streamable.com/cqyc7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fcqyc7&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzcorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=e5cd9f39\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/cqyc7</a></span><br />\n<strong>唔小心</strong>整到啲水落個大聲公度<br />\n<br />\nSSP街坊零衝擊被瘋狂拘捕<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://streamable.com/m2ie8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fm2ie8&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzcorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=6bcb398d\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/m2ie8</a></span><br />\n<br />\n沙田區議員王學禮被屈襲警全段經過<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://streamable.com/lqktr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Flqktr&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzcorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=88f6f70a\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/lqktr</a></span><br />\n<br />\nWTS少女要求警員出示委任證不果反被拘捕<br />\nBtw隻犬有啲似達哥。。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t3BGu7x.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft3BGu7x.gif&h=73b2c4ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/5abk0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2F5abk0&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzcorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=69b50fcb\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/5abk0</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/2zw3n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2F2zw3n&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzcorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=2c809a18\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/2zw3n</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/onccnews/videos/476982129755805/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fonccnews%2Fvideos%2F476982129755805%2F&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzcorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=be78f4f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/onccnews/videos/476982129755805/</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://streamable.com/vkum9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fvkum9&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzcorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=234b7e03\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/vkum9</a></span></strong>"},{"pid":"92be9cece553bd95d405db246d1bdfe7ff45723a","tid":1435063,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fafadac72936edeae0d3990a50d9d8bc85843b76","tid":1435063,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3d4df0bdfd12a2bf6d1885ab3194eecfda7979","tid":1435063,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c6c039e3da98669422b069568c5b78671969e1","tid":1435063,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ff734cd39eca216905d3d6d3157fd67e416604","tid":1435063,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:03:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif